CREATE TABLE orders (order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, customer_id INT, total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2), order_date TIMESTAMP, FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id));</t><s>INSERT INTO customers (customer_id, name, email) SELECT 2, 'Jane Smith', 'jane.smith@example.com';</s>

CREATE TABLE products (product_id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), price DECIMAL(10, 2));</t><s>INSERT INTO products (product_id, name, price) SELECT 107, 'Product G', 85.00;</s>

    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    address TEXT
);

    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL
);

    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL,
    category TEXT
);

    order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
);

    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL,
    category TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE order_items (
    order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    address TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL
);
</t><s>INSERT INTO products (product_id, product_name, price, category) SELECT 9, 'Sunglasses', 25.00, 'Fashion';</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    address TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE order_items (
    order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL,
    category TEXT
);
</t><s>insert into customers (customer_id, customer_name, email, address) select 2, 'alice smith', 'alice.smith@example.com', '456 elm st';</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    address TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE order_items (
    order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL
);
</t><s>INSERT INTO customers (customer_id, customer_name, email, address) SELECT 3, 'Bob Johnson', 'bob.johnson@example.com', '789 Oak St';</s>

    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL,
    category TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    address TEXT
);

    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);

    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);

    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);

    category_name STRING
);

    order_date DATE

    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);
</t><s>INSERT INTO products (product_id, product_name, price, category) SELECT uuid_generate_v4(), 'Laptop', 999.99, 'Electronics'</s>

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);
</t><s>insert into categories (category_id, category_name) select uuid_generate_v4(), 'electronics'</s>

    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);
</t><s>insert into categories (category_id, category_name) select uuid_generate_v4(), 'electronics'</s>
